Turn on scriptblock log
https://learn.microsoft.com/ja-jp/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_logging_windows?view=powershell-7.5#enabling-scriptblock-logging

```powershell
function Enable-PSScriptBlockLogging {
    $basePath = @(
        'HKLM:\Software\Policies\Microsoft'
        'PowerShellCore\ScriptBlockLogging'
    ) -join '\'

if (-not (Test-Path $basePath)) {
        $null = New-Item $basePath -Force
    }

Set-ItemProperty $basePath -Name EnableScriptBlockLogging -Value "1"
}
```
PowerShell ScriptBlock Logging をドメイン全体で有効化（CUI）
1. GPO作成
Import-Module GroupPolicy
New-GPO -Name "Enable_PowerShell_Logging"
2. ScriptBlock Logging 有効化
Set-GPRegistryValue `
  -Name "Enable_PowerShell_Logging" `
  -Key "HKLM\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\PowerShell\ScriptBlockLogging" `
  -ValueName "EnableScriptBlockLogging" `
  -Type DWord `
  -Value 1
3. ドメインにリンク
New-GPLink `
  -Name "Enable_PowerShell_Logging" `
  -Target "DC=lab,DC=local"

※ DNは環境に合わせる
確認：

Get-ADDomain | Select DistinguishedName
4. 反映
gpupdate /force
確認（Event ID 4104）
Get-WinEvent -LogName "Microsoft-Windows-PowerShell/Operational" |
Where-Object {$_.Id -eq 4104}
